As of 18th May 2012 I have ABANDONED this project
(wow, that was short-lived wasn't it?)

The rationale is that I have since seen better ways of doing much of what this
project contains.  For a start, just about everything within the Data namespace
is junk that I will never use again.  Anything of use in this project has been
ported over to:

